nodes.text: The siblipede was a non-sentient species of small insect native to Ithor, a planet in the Ottega sector of the Mid Rim. They often fed in groups upon the decaying leaves on the forest floor. Siblipedes were preyed on by manollium birds.
The siblipede was first mentioned in The Essential Atlas, a reference book written by Jason Fry and Daniel Wallace and published on August 18, 2009.
